ul  change  chg   prev close  open  days high  days low  volume  avg vol  wk high  wk low  full description berry global group inc formerly berry plastics group inc incorporated on november   is a provider of valueadded plastic consumer packaging nonwoven specialty materials and engineered materials the company offers products such as closures prescription vials specialty films adhesives nonwovens drink cups containers and bottles the company operates through three segments health hygiene  specialties consumer packaging and engineered materials the consumer packaging segment primarily consists of containers foodservice items closures overcaps bottles prescription vials tubes and printed films the health hygiene  specialties segment primarily consists of nonwoven specialty materials used in hygiene infection prevention personal care industrial construction and filtration applications the engineered materials segment primarily consists of pipeline corrosion protection solutions tapes and adhesives polyethylenebased film products can liners and specialty coated and laminated products the company offers its products to healthcare personal care and food and beverage industriesconsumer packagingthe company manufactures a range of branded container products which range from  ounces to  gallons and are offered in various styles with accompanying lids bails and handles as well as an array of decorating options the company is a provider of large size thermoformed polypropylene pp and injectionmolded plastic drink cups and lids the company is a producer of closures and overcaps across several of its product lines including continuousthread and childresistant closures as well as aerosol overcaps the company sells its closures into the markets including household chemical healthcare food and beverage and personal care the company offers a range of extruded and laminate tubes the company is a converter of printed bags pouches and rollstockengineered materialsthe company is a manufacturer of cloth and foil tape products other tape products include liners of splicing and laminating tapes flameretardant tapes vinylcoated and carton sealing tapes electrical doublefaced cloth masking mounting original equipment manufacturer oem and medical and specialty tapes the company sells a diversified portfolio of polyethylenebased film products to end users in the retail markets the companys products include drop cloths and retail trash bags the company is a manufacturer of polyvinyl chloride pvc films offering a range of pvc meat film in addition it offers a range of boxed products for food service and retail sales the company sells trashcan liners and food bags for offices restaurants schools hospitals hotels municipalities and manufacturing facilities the company manufactures both hand and machinewrap stretch films and shrink films which are used to prepare products and packages for storage and shipping it manufactures specialty coated and laminated products for healthcare industrial and military pouches roll wrap multiwall bags and fiber drum packaging industries the company produces anticorrosion products for infrastructure rehabilitation and pipeline projects throughout the world these products are used in oil gas and water supply and construction applicationshealth hygiene  specialtiesin the north america the company manufactures a range of products including baby diaper components feminine hygiene products substrates for dryer sheets medical garments materials household cleaning wipes filters and protective house wrap the company sells its products into the markets including personal care infection prevention and industrial construction and filtration applications in the south america the company sells components for baby diapers feminine hygiene specialty agriculture and industrial products in europe it offers a range of products and components of products for cable wrap baby diapers geosynthetics adult incontinence surgical drapes facemasks and 